{"tid":1287451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反送中示威者首遭起訴  法官令其不得保釋","createTime":"2019-07-05T08:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T08:22:32.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"820a0524b2f3dbc34238c6870e06b84f081fe033","tid":1287451,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:15:08.000Z","msg":"央視報導，香港東區裁判法院5日上午審理一起涉包圍香港員警總部及衝撞立法會案件。該男子被認為是首名被控的反送中示威者。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，一名31歲男子被指控參與6月21日包圍香港警察總部，以及7月1日衝擊香港立法會大樓，7月3日被警方拘捕，被控襲警、刑事毀壞及在公眾地方行為不檢罪。港媒指出，被告男子名叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n報導稱，目前法官將案件押後到8月2日再審，不得保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5cbfc2d1ef309a159100b8f476a9c05ef043814","tid":1287451,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:16:02.000Z","msg":"五毛可以用武漢分化我地，我地都可以利用武漢將把火燒上大陸，但記住唔係幫武漢，77當日要集中係五大訴求先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LvSJXSZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLvSJXSZ.png&h=0386e4d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db6b468e36ca416281b331a006bf244372e306c9","tid":1287451,"uid":156326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:16:23.000Z","msg":"要幫拖"},{"pid":"d7a52f30891e7e212d6063436c060d4e2e362166","tid":1287451,"uid":117276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:16:49.000Z","msg":"畫家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":